5
00:00:16,884 --> 00:00:18,184
<i>I might be just like you.</i>

6
00:00:19,676 --> 00:00:23,926
<i>Except from the time that I was a little girl, I knew that I could talk to the dead.</i>

7
00:00:24,907 --> 00:00:26,057
<i>It's all right, honey.</i>

8
00:00:26,122 --> 00:00:28,522
<i>Earthbound spirits, my grandmother called them,</i>

9
00:00:28,620 --> 00:00:32,171
<i>the ones who have not crossed over because they have unfinished business with the living,</i>

10
00:00:32,175 --> 00:00:33,671
<i>and they come to me for help.</i>

11
00:00:35,072 --> 00:00:37,745
<i>To tell you my story, I have to tell you theirs.</i>

12
00:00:56,734 --> 00:00:59,586
Everything is for sale except the buddha and those two paintings.

13
00:00:59,588 --> 00:01:01,526
