15
00:01:04,715 --> 00:01:06,070
That sounds fine. Excuse me.

16
00:01:06,076 --> 00:01:08,320
Hello? Oh, hey, Roger. Can you hold on one second?

17
00:01:08,325 --> 00:01:09,770
Can I show you the upstairs?

18
00:01:10,038 --> 00:01:11,513
Hello? No, I can't.

19
00:01:12,017 --> 00:01:13,163
3:00 is the latest.

20
