an established auction house like Sotheby's.

24
00:01:25,227 --> 00:01:27,323
Well, I don't have the time for all that.

25
00:01:27,365 --> 00:01:29,253
And actually, I'd rather do it locally.

26
00:01:29,265 --> 00:01:30,580
You know, support main street.

27
00:01:30,587 --> 00:01:33,682
