92
00:05:24,365 --> 00:05:26,461
Ok, you just completely lost my sympathy.

93
00:05:26,886 --> 00:05:28,981
- Excuse me, Miss.
- Hi. Can I help you?

94
00:05:33,425 --> 00:05:34,572
Hi. Is Christine here?

95
00:05:34,628 --> 00:05:36,430
Uh, no. She's out of town. She'll be back tomorrow night.

96
00:05:36,436 --> 00:05:38,651
