99
00:05:46,396 --> 00:05:48,160
Hi, sweetheart!

100
00:05:49,067 --> 00:05:50,441
Are you having your lunch?

101
00:05:50,607 --> 00:05:51,611
Oh! Sweet potatoes.

102
00:05:51,837 --> 00:05:52,732
My favorite.

103
