116
00:06:31,285 --> 00:06:32,113
Well, I...

117
00:06:32,116 --> 00:06:35,091
saw the room. She wouldn't let me go in, so I assumed that's something...

118
00:06:35,098 --> 00:06:37,073
I mean, losing a child?

119
00:06:39,086 --> 00:06:39,980
I don't know.

120
00:06:40,127 --> 00:06:42,320
I don't know how anybody ever gets over it.

121
