140
00:07:45,027 --> 00:07:46,773
You know what? This is ridiculous.

141
00:07:47,655 --> 00:07:50,400
Why don't you get somebody else to start taking some of bobby's shifts?

142
00:07:50,406 --> 00:07:52,101
Well, the truth is I volunteered.

143
00:07:52,605 --> 00:07:53,501
Why?

144
00:07:53,722 --> 00:07:56,525
I'm just trying to sock away some real money from that.

145
00:07:56,594 --> 00:07:58,196
- For what?
- The future.

146
00:07:58,808 --> 00:07:59,696
All right.

147
00:07:59,685 --> 00:08:01,423
I'm fully awake. I'm completely alert.

148
00:08:01,427 --> 00:08:02,781
Hey! Do you want me to make dinner?

149
00:08:02,786 --> 00:08:04,181
I lied. I must be dreaming.

150
00:08:04,667 --> 00:08:06,912
You know what? I'm starting to like cooking.

151
00:08:06,927 --> 00:08:10,540
If you weren't always hogging the kitchen, maybe I would get some practice.

152
00:08:10,548 --> 00:08:11,891
What do you want to drink.

153
00:08:12,075 --> 00:08:12,971
Beer is good.

154
00:08:14,966 --> 00:08:17,011
Remember  that customer I told you about?

155
00:08:17,345 --> 00:08:18,442
The fashion designer?

156
00:08:19,585 --> 00:08:21,662
Her kid died and I saw him today.

157
00:08:23,428 --> 00:08:24,161
Jim!

158
00:08:24,167 --> 00:08:25,031
Huh! Oh.

159
00:08:25,037 --> 00:08:25,932
What?

160
00:08:26,246 --> 00:08:27,570
I was just-- I was, um...

161
00:08:27,755 --> 00:08:29,072
trying to memorize, uh,

162
00:08:29,277 --> 00:08:31,670
the placement of all the furniture in the room.

163
00:08:32,078 --> 00:08:32,973
I'm awake.

164
00:08:34,155 --> 00:08:35,373
I'm really very awake.

165
00:08:37,118 --> 00:08:38,311
Let the machine get it.

166
00:08:42,537 --> 00:08:43,433
Hello?

167
00:08:43,936 --> 00:08:45,181
Who's watching the baby?

168
00:08:48,057 --> 00:08:48,953
Hey. Hey.

169
00:08:49,025 --> 00:08:50,372
You all right? Dinner? No?

170
00:08:50,648 --> 00:08:51,542
I'm sorry.

171
00:08:52,416 --> 00:08:54,562
- Can I help?
- I don't know. I love you.

172
00:08:56,615 --> 00:08:57,510
