177
00:09:12,248 --> 00:09:14,140
God. She treats me like I'm her wife.

178
00:09:15,156 --> 00:09:18,930
Yeah. She's got me doing the grocery shopping, picking up her dry cleaning.

179
00:09:18,936 --> 00:09:19,890
If she asked me to

180
00:09:20,846 --> 00:09:24,472
