255
00:14:57,287 --> 00:14:59,583
Well, I--I went back to your house earlier...

256
00:15:00,248 --> 00:15:02,153
to--to get my purse, um...

257
00:15:02,396 --> 00:15:04,343
because I'd left it behind, and, uh...

258
00:15:05,007 --> 00:15:06,600
I saw that Georgina had fallen.

259
00:15:07,827 --> 00:15:08,721
Is she ok?

260
00:15:09,057 --> 00:15:11,901
Yeah, she's gonna be fine. It was just a freak accident.

261
00:15:13,217 --> 00:15:16,411
